The informational and evaluational level of the system shall consist of at least the following information:
KRS numbers, names and levels of offenses;
Updates of information on:
Payment of fines;
Payment of costs;
Payment of restitution amounts;
Payment of court-ordered monetary penalties other than the above; and
Satisfaction of other types of court-ordered restitution;
Cases in which shock probation has been granted:
In such cases all information required for KRS 27A.410 and 27A.420 shall be entered for each case as an update to that person's file; and
Extracted data on shock probation shall be placed in the annual report of the Administrative Office of the Courts.
